A '''turbolaser blister''' was an architectural feature on the [[Dreadnaught-class heavy cruiser/Legends|''Dreadnaught''-class heavy cruiser]] which housed the ship's armament of [[Turbolaser/Legends|turbolasers]] as well as their control rooms and gunnery stations. During the Outbound Flight project, [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Jorus C'baoth]] thought that putting Jedi in charge of each of the six ships' turbolaser blisters, while taking part in a [[Force-meld|Jedi battle meld]] would result in the assemblage of [[Warship/Legends|warships]] becoming nearly invincible.

